<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Calvoro</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f9f9f9; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        .header { background-color: #1a1a1a; color: #ffffff; padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; }
        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
        .footer { background: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #888; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 14px 30px; background-color: #1a1a1a; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 20px; }
        .highlight { color: #f39c12; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>CALVORO</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Welcome to the inner circle, <span class="highlight"><%= username %></span>.</h2>
            <p>Thank you for joining Calvoro. We're excited to have you with us as we redefine luxury and style for the modern era.</p>
            <p>Your account is now active. You can start exploring our latest collections, track your orders, and manage your wishlist with ease.</p>
            
            <a href="<%= loginUrl %>" class="button">START EXPLORING</a>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">If you have any questions, simply reply to this email. Our concierge team is always here to help.</p>
            <p>Stay Classy,<br>The Calvoro Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2026 Calvoro International. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>You received this email because you signed up on calvoro.com.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
